    implication:"The Exp 238 distance-arithmetic confound is resolved: cost-neutralised coverage reveals a genuine non-saturating navigation bonus (mean +0.444/step, all-positive) that is the primary driver when pure coverage is penalised. The Rung-2 invasion looked like a wall escape, but was measured in growth phase — Exp 240 tests it at genuine demographic equilibrium.",
